### ðŸ« Lung Cancer Dataset

The **Lung Cancer dataset** used in this study was extracted from the **Prostate, Lung, Colorectal, and Ovarian (PLCO) Cancer Screening Trial**, a large-scale, multi-year study conducted by the U.S. National Cancer Institute (NCI).

